      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready for your dream ride? I\u2019m parting ways with this absolute gem, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape it still looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014spotless interior, gleaming paint, and it drives like a cloud. I\u2019ve taken so much pride in keeping this car perfect, and I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it just as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
