    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, boasting a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline with a recently overhauled double-VANOS system and preventative rod bearing replacement using high-performance shells. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate structural fatigue, ensuring the chassis handles the torque curve as intended. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a precise M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings, providing the telepathic feedback these cars are known for. Cosmetically and mechanically, this vehicle is in concours-ready, showroom condition with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
