    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. This car has never seen a winter road and remains in breathtaking condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, free of swirl marks, dings, or stone chips. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the trim remains as dark and supple as the day it was manufactured. Inside, the cabin is a literal time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is firm and scent-free, with no bolster wear or sun fading. All electronics, from the infotainment system to the smallest ambient light, function perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized centers with a 'no-expense-spared' philosophy, and I have the complete binder of records to prove it. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road grime. If you are looking for a flawless, collector-grade example that drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new car, this is it.",
      "price": 44500.0,
